import React from "react";

import {AppBar, Grid, Toolbar} from '@material-ui/core'

export const Navbar = () => {


    return (
        <AppBar position={"fixed"}>
            <Toolbar>
                <Grid container>
                    <Grid item>
                        Why Krabi
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item>
                        asds
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </Toolbar>
        </AppBar>
    )
}
